{"tid":1443242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣文宣 有活動喇","createTime":"2019-08-11T07:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T09:49:44.000Z","uid":277735,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f21680c9e7eed67dfcaf122e8a569d5b67fec54","tid":1443242,"uid":277735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:20:32.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲想係青衣做多啲文宣<br />\n例如派下傳單 播下啲改編歌 做下放映會 等等<br />\n做多啲宣傳工作 大家一齊討論下<br />\n<br />\n之前出左次post 已經有二十個人係group<br />\n想有更多人幫手<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動係持久戰 要keep住有文宣好重要<br />\n我地已經無輸既成本。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RVwv7nS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRVwv7nS.jpg&h=b9d694dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面係TG group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=f4c1965f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n利申： 住左係長發廿幾年， 無搞過呢啲野既經驗 只係時再做多啲野。"},{"pid":"11d858567814e5938b7ea8d1f3aa1c35845e6391","tid":1443242,"uid":277735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:20:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"51d2f1a09dab585ca49f9d4491f04289026e2225","tid":1443242,"uid":277735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"97c159dd17bcd3f5a815faef3c077ab59a9ffeae","tid":1443242,"uid":277735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"b6ed1fe8175716202b066c153019010e4f27ad85","tid":1443242,"uid":277735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:23:25.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"0c0f81b910ecf4c2af036f47e7370cce809df743","tid":1443242,"uid":280821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"